# Docs & tooling pointers (Sections R & T)

## Where things live

- **Hub:** root `CLAUDE.md`; **[`AGENTS.md`](../../AGENTS.md)** (agent conduct, skills activation, Pint/PHPUnit habits); Claude entry: `.claude/CLAUDE.md` → hub + **`.claude/rules/bedrock-sage-bootstrap.md`** (mirror contract, sync, **`./scripts/check-agent-mirrors.sh`**, pre-commit, CI).
- **Cursor:** `.cursor/rules/*.mdc`, `.cursor/skills/`; root `.cursorrules` → rules + hub.
- **MCP:** keep `.mcp.json` and `.cursor/mcp.json` aligned — see **`docs/mcp.md`** (WP-CLI/Acorn server lives in **`scripts/mcp-wp-acorn/`**).
- **UI kit catalog:** **`docs/components/INDEX.md`** (**Shadpine UI**); hub **`docs/INDEX.md`**.
- **Product context:** `.claude/rules/site-product.md` and **`project-memory.md`** (optional per clone; not mirrored from `.cursor/`).

## Quick rule routing

- **Tokens / template identity:** **`00-template-context.mdc`** (`{THEME_SLUG}`, `{DEV_HOST}`).
- **Theme PHP / Blade / ACF / Support / Integrations / Features:** **`05-theme-php-blade-acf.mdc`**; flexible tests **`10-testing-mandatory.mdc`**; blocks **`12-acf-blocks.mdc`**.
- **Alpine + TS + Vite + a11y:** **`06-theme-alpine-vite.mdc`**; optional **`docs/frontend-alpine.md`** when present.
- **Shadpine UI (Alpine + Blade in this repo):** **`14-shadpine-ui.mdc`**, skill **`shadpine-ui`**.
- **First-party plugins:** **`04-wordpress-plugins.mdc`**, skill **`wordpress-plugins`**.
- **Conduct, verify-before-done, ULTRATHINK, APIs:** **`01-global-protocols.mdc`**.
- **Tests + lint + Prettier:** **`10-testing-mandatory.mdc`**, **`13-mandatory-lint.mdc`**, **`11-frontend-formatting.mdc`**.

## Optional docs (when you maintain them)

- **`docs/quality-audits.md`** — recurring PHP/TS/a11y cadence alongside mandatory theme checks (**`10-testing-mandatory.mdc`**).
- **`docs/errors/`**, **`docs/warnings/`** — fix root cause; correlate downstream; prefer tests (**`10-testing-mandatory.mdc`**).
- **External APIs** — discover shape before coding; document in **`docs/API.md`** / **`docs/overview.md`**; mutations per **`01-global-protocols.mdc`**.

