## Docs hygiene

`docs/INDEX.md` — no orphaned docs. Stack commands & rule index: root `CLAUDE.md`. Changes to **`.cursor/rules/`**, root **`CLAUDE.md`**, or agent hubs → same commit as behavior when possible. Recurring mistakes → extend **`docs/`** or add a bullet under **Quick rule routing** / this file.

## Section T (`.cursorrules`)

Authoritative detail: `.cursor/rules/*.mdc`. MCP: `.cursor/mcp.json`. Hub: `CLAUDE.md`.

